26
00:01:29,094 --> 00:01:33,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Here come the Noizy Tribe, we're back!</i></b></font>

27
00:02:00,464 --> 00:02:02,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One, two...!</b></font>

28
00:02:13,144 --> 00:02:19,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's this all about? Joshima and
