29
00:02:19,484 --> 00:02:22,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The biggest names of Purple
Shadow coming together...</b></font>

30
00:02:22,154 --> 00:02:24,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what's going on.</b></font>

31
00:02:24,054 --> 00:02:27,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't you know? Project D is coming.</b></font>

32
00:02:27,524 --> 00:02:32,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D? So Joshima and
Hoshino plan to take them on?</b></font>

33
00:02:32,594 --> 00:02:38,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, no way. One of the younger members
