35
00:02:43,074 --> 00:02:45,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're gods!</b></font>

36
00:02:52,584 --> 00:02:58,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're here! "God Arm"Toshiya Joshima
