40
00:03:22,944 --> 00:03:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Also, I make it a point
not to listen to my doctor.</b></font>

41
00:03:27,914 --> 00:03:30,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a good one!</b></font>

42
00:03:30,114 --> 00:03:34,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Project D, huh? It's been a while
since I've felt my blood race.</b></font>

43
00:03:34,894 --> 00:03:38,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This may be the folly of a couple
of middle-aged street racers,</b></font>

44
00:03:38,464 --> 00:03:40,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I'm looking forward to it.</b></font>

45
00:03:41,734 --> 00:03:46,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 19: God Foot and God Arm"</b></font>

46
00:03:50,274 --> 00:03:54,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mr. Joshima, Mr. Hoshino,
do you really intend to participate?</b></font>

47
00:03:54,114 --> 00:03:55,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In this upcoming race...</b></font>

48
00:03:55,244 --> 00:03:58,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You bet. Something strange about that?</b></font>

49
00:03:58,114 --> 00:04:01,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not "strange," but...</b></font>

50
00:04:01,654 --> 00:04:04,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Our opponents are basically kids,</b></font>

51
00:04:04,084 --> 00:04:06,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so there's no need for you,
our seniors, to participate.</b></font>

52
00:04:06,154 --> 00:04:08,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, age has nothing to do with it.</b></font>

53
00:04:08,494 --> 00:04:11,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These folks are kind enough
to come here from Gunma,</b></font>

54
00:04:11,364 --> 00:04:15,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so responding in kind is just a matter
of common courtesy, don't you think?</b></font>

55
00:04:15,794 --> 00:04:19,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>True, they're coming all the way here,
but it's not as if we asked them to...</b></font>

56
00:04:19,634 --> 00:04:21,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>C'mon, don't say that.</b></font>

57
00:04:21,674 --> 00:04:26,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In this case, just keep quiet
and let us do it our way.</b></font>

58
00:04:26,044 --> 00:04:32,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not as if we're vain enough to think
we're the absolute greatest there is.</b></font>

59
00:04:32,184 --> 00:04:37,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When Purple Shadow was first formed,
we taught you guys a lot of different things,</b></font>

60
00:04:37,454 --> 00:04:41,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but now, I don't think we could
even keep up with you youngsters.</b></font>

61
00:04:41,554 --> 00:04:47,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You must be joking, Mr. Hoshino!
We still don't even come close to you!</b></font>

62
00:04:47,064 --> 00:04:51,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, don't be so modest.
You've stood on the winner's podium</b></font>

63
00:04:51,734 --> 00:04:54,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at the Tsukuba amateur circuit
race any number of times.</b></font>

64
00:04:54,234 --> 00:04:57,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We really like this sort of thing.</b></font>

65
00:04:57,244 --> 00:05:00,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even at our age, it makes us feel like kids.</b></font>

66
00:05:00,574 --> 00:05:03,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay then, should we bang out
two or three more laps?</b></font>

67
00:05:03,714 --> 00:05:08,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Gotta shake off some
more of these cobwebs, huh?</b></font>

68
00:05:28,334 --> 00:05:32,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Honestly, what a joke. "Cobwebs," my foot.</b></font>

69
00:05:32,444 --> 00:05:36,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those two are always polished
to razor-sharp precision.</b></font>

70
00:05:41,714 --> 00:05:48,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>God Arm, so named for his
godlike handling capabilities...</b></font>

71
00:05:48,094 --> 00:05:50,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Toshiya Joshima.</b></font>

72
00:05:54,564 --> 00:05:58,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And God Foot,</b></font>

73
00:05:58,064 --> 00:06:02,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>named for his superhuman
ability to work the accelerator...</b></font>

74
00:06:02,804 --> 00:06:05,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kozo Hoshino.</b></font>

75
00:06:05,374 --> 00:06:08,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They've fought their way through
countless fierce battles...</b></font>

76
00:06:08,444 --> 00:06:10,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're the gods of the mountain pass!</b></font>

77
00:06:17,754 --> 00:06:21,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

78
00:06:24,724 --> 00:06:27,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is Pops not home?</b></font>

79
00:06:29,264 --> 00:06:31,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Jeez...</b></font>

80
00:06:31,334 --> 00:06:33,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, Fujiwara Tofu Shop.</b></font>

81
00:06:33,904 --> 00:06:36,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is Wataru.</b></font>

82
00:06:36,104 --> 00:06:39,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm in the area. You wanna
get something to eat?</b></font>

83
00:06:43,614 --> 00:06:46,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So? Where to next?</b></font>

84
00:06:46,414 --> 00:06:47,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ibaraki.</b></font>

85
00:06:47,584 --> 00:06:49,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah.</b></font>

86
00:06:50,624 --> 00:06:52,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

87
00:06:52,354 --> 00:06:58,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really am grateful to you. I feel like
you've given me an important hint.</b></font>

88
00:06:58,194 --> 00:07:01,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It makes me happy to hear that.</b></font>

89
00:07:01,094 --> 00:07:05,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Recently, I feel like I've finally
started to understand the Eight-Six.</b></font>

90
00:07:05,804 --> 00:07:07,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

91
00:07:07,204 --> 00:07:10,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There it is, the spacey side of him...</i></b></font>

92
00:07:10,604 --> 00:07:14,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We normal folk can't understand
what you say sometimes.</b></font>

93
00:07:14,714 --> 00:07:18,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But it's true! I've come to sort of understand it...</b></font>

94
00:07:18,314 --> 00:07:23,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...how to race in order to bring out
the Eight-Six's full potential.</b></font>

95
00:07:23,384 --> 00:07:27,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What I should do when tackling
a course for the first time...</b></font>

96
00:07:27,954 --> 00:07:30,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How to get the right
underbody balance point...</b></font>

97
00:07:30,794 --> 00:07:36,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One by one, I've gradually come
to understand those things.</b></font>

98
00:07:36,334 --> 00:07:39,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I guess that's what they call progress.</b></font>

99
00:07:39,564 --> 00:07:46,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Me, I don't see how you've been able to
race like this without knowing anything.</b></font>

100
00:07:46,204 --> 00:07:48,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I might lose someday...</b></font>

101
00:07:48,244 --> 00:07:53,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if that day comes, I think
by then I will have learned more.</b></font>

102
00:07:53,644 --> 00:07:55,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About the Eight-Six...</b></font>

103
00:08:13,404 --> 00:08:18,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's this all about? There's
one more support van this time.</b></font>

104
00:08:18,174 --> 00:08:21,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke and I wrote up a list
of the things we'll need,</b></font>

105
00:08:21,874 --> 00:08:25,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and thought that three vans
wouldn't quite be enough.</b></font>

106
00:08:25,584 --> 00:08:29,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the kind of formidable
opponent we'll be facing.</b></font>

107
00:08:29,284 --> 00:08:32,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's simplest just to think about it that way.</b></font>

108
00:08:32,684 --> 00:08:36,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll be traveling a long way
this time, so everyone drive safely.</b></font>

109
00:08:36,294 --> 00:08:37,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right!</b></font>

110
00:08:47,034 --> 00:08:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's head out!</b></font>

111
00:08:53,104 --> 00:08:57,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss, did you hear?
Project D's next opponent...</b></font>

112
00:08:57,414 --> 00:09:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is Purple Shadow in Ibaraki.</b></font>

113
00:09:02,954 --> 00:09:04,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh.</b></font>

114
00:09:04,454 --> 00:09:08,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's more, Kozo Hoshino and
Toshiya Joshima will face them.</b></font>

115
00:09:10,324 --> 00:09:13,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's a surprise.</b></font>

116
00:09:13,124 --> 00:09:16,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you two have time...</b></font>

117
00:09:16,334 --> 00:09:19,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...you should go watch that race.</b></font>

118
00:09:19,734 --> 00:09:22,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is Purple Shadow really that good?</b></font>

119
00:09:22,604 --> 00:09:25,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Daiki, you may not know this,</b></font>

120
00:09:25,504 --> 00:09:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but even Mr. Toudou acknowledges
Hoshino and Joshima as his betters.</b></font>

121
00:09:29,244 --> 00:09:31,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way...</b></font>

122
00:09:31,014 --> 00:09:34,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sir, do you think Project D
has a chance of winning?</b></font>

123
00:09:34,684 --> 00:09:39,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Every race boils down to luck.
No one knows what'll happen.</b></font>

124
00:09:39,524 --> 00:09:41,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rather than tryin' to
predict somethin' like that,</b></font>

125
00:09:41,254 --> 00:09:44,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you should think about how
<i>you</i> would take them on,</b></font>

126
00:09:44,464 --> 00:09:49,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>then watch what Project D does to face
the giant wall that stands before them.</b></font>

127
00:09:49,534 --> 00:09:52,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It should be a good learnin' experience.</b></font>

128
00:10:04,014 --> 00:10:05,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here they are!</b></font>

129
00:10:25,234 --> 00:10:29,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"National Park"</b></font>

130
00:10:25,234 --> 00:10:29,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Touge View Park"</b></font>

131
00:10:28,504 --> 00:10:33,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Understood. We'll do our part to
make sure things run smoothly.</b></font>

132
00:10:33,974 --> 00:10:36,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much.</b></font>

133
00:10:36,214 --> 00:10:38,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you for your cooperation.</b></font>

134
00:10:41,154 --> 00:10:45,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh. They're a nice bunch
of young men, very polite.</b></font>

135
00:10:45,354 --> 00:10:47,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Agreed.</b></font>

136
00:10:47,024 --> 00:10:52,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Their homepage is a bit confrontational,
so I thought they'd be cocky little brats.</b></font>

137
00:10:52,524 --> 00:10:54,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I like these guys.</b></font>

138
00:10:54,164 --> 00:11:00,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In return, I'll do them the courtesy
of giving this challenge my all.</b></font>

139
00:11:00,064 --> 00:11:04,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For the first time in a while...
this looks like it'll be a good night.</b></font>

140
00:11:04,544 --> 00:11:08,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As always, five laps at 80%.</b></font>

141
00:11:08,544 --> 00:11:10,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Be sure and concentrate.</b></font>

142
00:12:04,434 --> 00:12:06,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Incredible...</b></font>

143
00:12:06,734 --> 00:12:12,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Van #4 is filled mostly with spare tires!</b></font>

144
00:12:12,804 --> 00:12:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And one moped? What would we use this for?</b></font>

145
00:12:17,014 --> 00:12:19,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, that's for the drivers to use.</b></font>

146
00:12:19,144 --> 00:12:20,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The drivers?</b></font>

147
00:12:20,484 --> 00:12:25,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I'd have them scout the course
tomorrow evening while it's still light.</b></font>

148
00:12:25,684 --> 00:12:28,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Apparently, a moped makes
it easy to spot fractures</b></font>

149
00:12:28,154 --> 00:12:31,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or small slopes in the road surface.</b></font>

150
00:12:31,964 --> 00:12:36,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That way, you can come up with strategies for
courses where the slightest variable counts.</b></font>

151
00:12:36,634 --> 00:12:39,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Walking the course is really the best way,</b></font>

152
00:12:39,034 --> 00:12:40,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but this is what Ryosuke came up with,</b></font>

153
00:12:40,934 --> 00:12:44,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>one of the new approaches
we'll be using from now on.</b></font>

154
00:12:44,174 --> 00:12:48,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get it. Ryosuke sure does
think up a lot of ideas.</b></font>

155
00:12:48,014 --> 00:12:50,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I suppose this means if we stick
with the same approach as always,</b></font>

156
00:12:50,174 --> 00:12:52,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>we won't be able to win...</b></font>

157
00:13:02,224 --> 00:13:04,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now it's okay!</b></font>

158
00:13:04,664 --> 00:13:06,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I think this tire balance will
give you a good clean ride.</b></font>

159
00:13:06,894 --> 00:13:10,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just be sure to keep a close eye on traction.</b></font>

160
00:13:10,294 --> 00:13:12,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Here I go.</b></font>

161
00:13:17,204 --> 00:13:19,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How is it, Matsumoto?</b></font>

162
00:13:19,244 --> 00:13:23,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's in great shape.
Fujiwara's in fine form as well, eh?</b></font>

163
00:13:23,574 --> 00:13:28,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even the settings he requested make it
seem like he's got a handle on something.</b></font>

164
00:13:28,654 --> 00:13:30,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's different from how he used to be.</b></font>

165
00:13:30,554 --> 00:13:32,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel that as well.</b></font>

166
00:13:32,424 --> 00:13:37,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There were times in the Saitama
area when he was quite conflicted.</b></font>

167
00:13:37,224 --> 00:13:42,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even outside of D's activities, Fujiwara has
been practicing, in ways we haven't seen.</b></font>

168
00:13:42,994 --> 00:13:46,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He is definitely getting a handle on something.</b></font>

169
00:13:46,334 --> 00:13:50,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In this race, regardless of
whether he wins or loses,</b></font>

170
00:13:50,034 --> 00:13:54,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he will experience sudden
explosive growth, Matsumoto.</b></font>

171
00:14:18,704 --> 00:14:23,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, Keisuke's FD
sure has gotten flashy.</b></font>

172
00:14:23,234 --> 00:14:27,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For your information, the exterior
is 100% to Keisuke's taste.</b></font>

173
00:14:27,644 --> 00:14:28,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How is it?</b></font>

174
00:14:28,944 --> 00:14:30,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The slopes are steeper than I'd thought,</b></font>

175
00:14:30,984 --> 00:14:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so this tire balance relies too much on the rear.</b></font>

176
00:14:33,214 --> 00:14:35,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Should we raise the back area a bit?</b></font>

177
00:14:35,314 --> 00:14:37,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please do.</b></font>

178
00:14:41,754 --> 00:14:46,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you Keisuke Takahashi, driver of the FD?</b></font>

179
00:14:49,264 --> 00:14:54,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're quite the looker.
I bet chicks dig you, huh?</b></font>

180
00:14:55,434 --> 00:14:58,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was a hit with the ladies
when I was younger, too.</b></font>

181
00:14:58,504 --> 00:15:01,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A guy like that's got an aura,
something you can instantly tell.</b></font>

182
00:15:01,944 --> 00:15:05,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Youth is somethin' you can't get back.</b></font>

183
00:15:05,784 --> 00:15:10,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once I hit middle age, I got all this
activity around the belly here,</b></font>

184
00:15:10,154 --> 00:15:12,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and getting the young ladies
to turn 'round and look</b></font>

185
00:15:12,824 --> 00:15:16,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>takes so much effort it makes you wanna cry.</b></font>

186
00:15:16,494 --> 00:15:19,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And then there's the extra
money you've gotta spend!</b></font>

187
00:15:19,524 --> 00:15:21,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still...</b></font>

188
00:15:21,664 --> 00:15:25,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I score me some sweet
thing after all that effort,</b></font>

189
00:15:25,704 --> 00:15:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel a kind of happiness I never
could've known in my younger days!</b></font>

190
00:15:32,004 --> 00:15:36,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, one day you'll understand.</b></font>

191
00:15:36,144 --> 00:15:39,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You've gotta play the field while you're young.</b></font>

192
00:15:39,684 --> 00:15:42,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See ya.</b></font>

193
00:15:42,114 --> 00:15:46,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, wait. I almost forgot
what I really wanted to say.</b></font>

194
00:15:46,524 --> 00:15:49,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got an important proposal
to make about tomorrow's race.</b></font>

195
00:15:49,194 --> 00:15:51,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Proposal? What is it?</b></font>

196
00:15:51,364 --> 00:15:53,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How should I put this...?</b></font>

197
00:15:53,464 --> 00:15:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Normally, a mountain pass
has an uphill and a downhill.</b></font>

198
00:15:57,464 --> 00:16:02,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In my case, I haven't tuned my car
thinking only about the uphill...</b></font>

199
00:16:02,034 --> 00:16:06,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Aiming for total balance is
the mark of a true racer, right?</b></font>

200
00:16:06,174 --> 00:16:10,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's where my proposal
comes in. For just our race,</b></font>

201
00:16:10,014 --> 00:16:13,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>what do you say we opt
against an uphill-only stage?</b></font>

202
00:16:13,644 --> 00:16:19,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You mean, race on a stage that
combines uphill and downhill?</b></font>

203
00:16:19,424 --> 00:16:20,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's what I mean.</b></font>

204
00:16:20,854 --> 00:16:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If that's how this is going to be,</i></b></font>

205
00:16:23,154 --> 00:16:26,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'd like to show off some of</i>
<i>my killer downhill techniques.</i></b></font>

206
00:16:28,434 --> 00:16:33,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. I accept your proposal. With pleasure.</b></font>

207
00:16:33,064 --> 00:16:36,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes! I appreciate that.
I look forward to our race.</b></font>

208
00:16:36,504 --> 00:16:39,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, and one more thing.</b></font>

209
00:16:39,844 --> 00:16:42,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can we do our race first?</b></font>

210
00:16:42,914 --> 00:16:44,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Before the downhill?</b></font>

211
00:16:44,944 --> 00:16:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get more fired up that way.
I'm the impatient type.</b></font>

212
00:16:49,514 --> 00:16:52,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Waitin' just drives me crazy.</b></font>

213
00:16:52,284 --> 00:16:55,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine. That's okay as well.</b></font>

214
00:16:55,254 --> 00:16:59,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay! Well, that's that,
and I'm lookin' forward to it!</b></font>

215
00:17:00,624 --> 00:17:02,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See ya!</b></font>

216
00:17:06,634 --> 00:17:09,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Was that a bad move, brother?</b></font>

217
00:17:09,034 --> 00:17:12,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't think I had any reason to refuse.</b></font>

218
00:17:12,374 --> 00:17:16,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's fine. It was an unexpected
proposal, but sure enough,</b></font>

219
00:17:16,414 --> 00:17:18,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there was no reason to refuse...</b></font>

220
00:17:18,744 --> 00:17:25,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Rather than being disadvantageous,
his proposal in fact counts in our favor.</b></font>

221
00:17:25,884 --> 00:17:32,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I take my hat off to him. He casually
made us a most fair proposition.</b></font>

222
00:17:32,164 --> 00:17:34,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He is a formidable opponent, Keisuke.</b></font>

223
00:17:44,174 --> 00:17:49,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I feel like... sort of invigorated.</i>
<i>It's been a while since I've felt this!</i></b></font>

224
00:17:54,144 --> 00:17:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like I could lose...</i></b></font>

225
00:17:56,154 --> 00:17:58,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That old dude is something else!</i></b></font>

226
00:18:01,254 --> 00:18:06,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What is this? I feel so much</i>
<i>pressure. Far more than usual!</i></b></font>

227
00:18:11,534 --> 00:18:14,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This will be one incredible race!</i></b></font>

228
00:18:24,684 --> 00:18:27,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Man, I'm tired!</b></font>

229
00:18:27,144 --> 00:18:30,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said it.</b></font>

230
00:18:30,014 --> 00:18:32,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, Fujiwara.</b></font>

231
00:18:34,184 --> 00:18:35,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You two will be staying</b></font>

232
00:18:35,694 --> 00:18:38,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at a bed-and-breakfast
at the foot of the mountain.</b></font>

233
00:18:38,064 --> 00:18:39,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A bed-and-breakfast?</b></font>

234
00:18:39,224 --> 00:18:42,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. You can get a good night's
rest in an air-conditioned room.</b></font>

235
00:18:42,994 --> 00:18:45,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's fine and all, but why just us?</b></font>

236
00:18:45,734 --> 00:18:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It should be obvious.
Because you're the drivers.</b></font>

237
00:18:48,974 --> 00:18:51,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way! I'm fine without!</b></font>

238
00:18:51,504 --> 00:18:53,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll sleep in my car as always.</b></font>

239
00:18:53,644 --> 00:18:56,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke, please take the room in my place.</b></font>

240
00:18:56,014 --> 00:19:01,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, Fujiwara. This is my order as team leader.</b></font>

241
00:19:01,654 --> 00:19:06,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We are in that season. With days as hot
as these, one can hardly sleep inside a car.</b></font>

242
00:19:06,754 --> 00:19:10,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's important you be rested to
preserve your powers of concentration</b></font>

243
00:19:10,154 --> 00:19:12,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for tomorrow's race.</b></font>

244
00:19:12,394 --> 00:19:16,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Getting a good night's rest
is for the sake of the team!</b></font>

245
00:19:16,394 --> 00:19:20,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll take you to the bed-and-breakfast,
so grab your things and get into Van #1.</b></font>

246
00:19:26,204 --> 00:19:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fumihiro said he'll come get us around 4:00.</b></font>

247
00:19:29,244 --> 00:19:32,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll be able to get quite
a bit of sleep, won't we?</b></font>

248
00:19:35,554 --> 00:19:39,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I feel bad for the others,</b></font>

249
00:19:39,084 --> 00:19:43,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I sure am grateful to be able to
stretch my legs and sleep like this.</b></font>

250
00:19:43,254 --> 00:19:49,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You said it. This is the first time, isn't it?
Since we've started D's expeditions.</b></font>

251
00:19:49,534 --> 00:19:54,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, this course will make it
hard to go on the offensive.</b></font>

252
00:19:54,264 --> 00:19:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's pretty short, but it has some
points that're hard to nail down.</b></font>

253
00:19:58,074 --> 00:20:02,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There are lots of corners with lazy turns
and no visible exit point, aren't there?</b></font>

254
00:20:02,474 --> 00:20:08,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The roads have lots of twists... It doesn't
seem like a race that'll be settled soon.</b></font>

255
00:20:12,984 --> 00:20:17,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That was fast! The idiot's already asleep!</i></b></font>

256
00:20:17,094 --> 00:20:20,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Does he not feel pressure or anything?</i></b></font>

257
00:20:20,924 --> 00:20:25,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He looks like a pushover, but he's</i>
<i>got an irritatingly tough core.</i></b></font>

258
00:20:25,964 --> 00:20:29,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm way more sensitive...</i></b></font>

259
00:20:34,814 --> 00:20:37,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is that boy Kenta doing?</b></font>

260
00:20:37,474 --> 00:20:40,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He said he put some tanning oil on
and was going to get some sun.</b></font>

261
00:20:40,244 --> 00:20:44,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Idiot. What does he want to get any darker for?</b></font>

262
00:20:44,924 --> 00:20:48,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, these days sure have gotten hot.</b></font>

263
00:20:48,254 --> 00:20:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Being inside our cars
would be unbearable, huh?</b></font>

264
00:20:50,954 --> 00:20:56,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was a good call, having Keisuke
and Fujiwara rest someplace cool.</b></font>

265
00:20:56,464 --> 00:21:02,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's right. This race will require
peak physical and mental strength.</b></font>

266
00:21:02,774 --> 00:21:08,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He even thought this part through.
That's Ryosuke for you.</b></font>

267
00:21:08,644 --> 00:21:11,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, indeed...</b></font>

268
00:21:54,154 --> 00:21:58,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara sure is taking his
sweet time inspecting the course.</b></font>

269
00:21:58,164 --> 00:22:00,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't seem to be coming back, does he?</b></font>

270
00:22:00,364 --> 00:22:04,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke breezed through it
and was back in about 15 minutes.</b></font>

271
00:22:04,064 --> 00:22:06,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a competition, you know.</b></font>

272
00:22:07,704 --> 00:22:12,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got my own pace. I may be fast,
but I saw what I needed to see.</b></font>

273
00:22:12,344 --> 00:22:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, do your best. You'll be racing first today.</b></font>

274
00:22:17,014 --> 00:22:18,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just leave it to me!</b></font>

275
00:22:18,744 --> 00:22:22,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I slept nice and cool,
and my body's in top form!</b></font>

276
00:22:56,754 --> 00:23:00,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's about to start. Tonight is a big event!</b></font>

277
00:23:00,584 --> 00:23:03,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Just having Joshima and Hoshino participate</b></font>

278
00:23:03,594 --> 00:23:06,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in this kind of event makes it big enough!</b></font>

279
00:23:06,564 --> 00:23:09,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Those guys are legends in their own time!</b></font>

280
00:23:09,494 --> 00:23:13,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Seriously, what do you think about Project D?</b></font>

281
00:23:13,134 --> 00:23:17,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can their drivers compete with the
duo that people refer to as gods?!</b></font>

282
00:23:17,134 --> 00:23:20,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're no ordinary racers, that's for sure.</b></font>

283
00:23:20,104 --> 00:23:24,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both of them are young guys still in their 20s,</b></font>

284
00:23:24,074 --> 00:23:27,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but they've been to all the
mountain passes in northern Kanto</b></font>

285
00:23:27,484 --> 00:23:30,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and have never lost once.</b></font>

286
00:23:30,314 --> 00:23:32,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Then they'd better give it their all.</b></font>

287
00:23:32,924 --> 00:23:36,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, we came here to watch the gods race!</b></font>

288
00:23:37,524 --> 00:23:39,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There sure are a lot of onlookers.</b></font>

289
00:23:39,824 --> 00:23:44,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Having too many people
here would just cause problems,</b></font>

290
00:23:44,194 --> 00:23:50,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so apparently D didn't advertise the time
and place on their homepage this time.</b></font>

291
00:23:50,204 --> 00:23:54,944
